Who: CYCLONUS, DEEPSTRYKE, PHOBIA, NIGHTRAZOR, Hydras, Perceptor
Location: Black Fortress - Throne Room

> "Yes i recognize them, Cyclonus... and their skills are quite
> impressive"said sincerely impressing"And yes, i capture the two Autobots
> leaders...."
>
> Sensing that this could be a very sensitive information Perceptor, walked
> toward Cyclonus and whisper him "We should insolate the area... No comlinks
> in or out while this talk is done"

Cyclonus nodded once as he quickly walked over to one of the control
panels on the side and activated a radio dampening field over the
room. there would be no communications into or out of the room except
through that panel. Cyclonus stood there to monitor the panel, in case
anyone had a call for Huydras or anyone else.

(OOC: In other words, if you try to call anyone to or fromthe throne
room the call gets fowarded to the panel instead of where it was
suppose to go)

> "One of them fell in my trap and the other was capturing while he attamped
> to rescu him... and more over five low rank Autobots and maximals are in my
> grasp right now, among prisioners and reprogramed, not counting the
> leaders." said proudly the predacon leader

Deepstryke straightened, obviously impressed. "It would seem that
Cyclonus has indeed chosen well. Soon you would have this whole planet
and beyond under your dominion." The large mech said, his voice deep
and booming.

"Yes" said the female as she sauntered up next to Deepstryke and
rested a hand on his broad shoulder, "Unicron seems to have no need
for us, I think this place would be rather nice." She turned and
smiled at Hydras as she looked at him speculatively.

"Now that you have the Autobots, what is your plan of attack now, it
would seem that you have the means to do a great many more things?"
Deepstryke said as he smiled.

Cyclonus stepped foward a step from the panel, he glanced at Hydras
and then spoke, "I think I may have something that could help with
that." Cyclonus looked at the others, "If Hydras agrees, we could once
again attempt to recreate the sweep army we had once before, and then
with all of our combined power we would brush all the rest of the
Autobots and Maximals from this entire planet."

(TAG)

Preston
